title: ERROR  run failed: command  exited (137) during build
body:
**Describe the bug**

I'm trying to run pnpm build in WSL but I get this error:

`Tasks:    4 successful, 141 total
Cached:    4 cached, 141 total
  Time:    1m34.98s
Failed:    @elizaos/plugin-arbitrage#build

 ERROR  run failed: command  exited (137)
 ELIFECYCLE  Command failed with exit code 137.`

**To Reproduce**

I am running WSL on Windows 11. I ran this command:
`pnpm build`

**Expected behavior**

I should be able to finish the build without error
